                skos:exactMatch <http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/TelecommunicationNetworkIdentifier> ;
                skos:scopeNote """Superclass of TelephoneNumber (ent00000023) and EmailAddress (ent00000024). 
